<div class="gem-c-govspeak govuk-govspeak " data-module="govspeak">
      <div class="govspeak">
<p>DCMS and our Public Bodies produce Official Statistics covering our sectors. Details of recently published and upcoming releases are available on our <a href="https://www.gov.uk/government/collections/statistics">Official Statistics catalogue page</a>.</p>

